schools.name: Vaux HS: A Big Picture School

data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4 bedroom home located in the desirable Fairmount/Art Museum neighborhood.  Upon entering, you will be greeted by an open concept living room, beautiful hardwood flooring, tall ceilings, and neutral paint colors. You will appreciate the exposed brick walls enhancing the character and charm throughout the home. Continue through the downstairs to the separate dining area complete with updated powder room. The large kitchen boasts timeless cabinetry, beautiful granite countertops and stainless steel appliances.  The second floor contains 3 spacious bedrooms and a beautifully renovated tiled bathroom. The 3rd floor offers a large main bedroom with a bonus space that has the potential of a 5th bedroom, large walk in closet or en-suite. There is a spacious backyard perfect for entertaining or simply relaxing in your own private oasis. This location is in walking distance to  parks, museums, restaurants and Kelly Drive with easy access to highways and public transportation. Additional bonuses include over 2,000sq feet of living space and newer HVAC system with central heating and air.  Schedule your tour and experience all the reasons to love N. 28th St!
